{"tid":276840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯代表律師懷疑歧視黃種人　指慶幸案件由裁判官官審理：除非你是黃色","createTime":"2017-06-09T06:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T01:47:30.000Z","uid":11001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3388b3fb84d0b0100dc1c1bf7c6028b50a4b77f","tid":276840,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1496982034_4576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1496982034_4576.jpg&h=32dbb400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告朱經緯及其代表大狀彭彼得(左)(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n雨傘運動期間涉揮動警棍襲途人的退休警司朱經緯，被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院預審。代表朱經緯的大律師彭彼得在庭上稱，慶幸案件不用經陪審團審訊，而是於裁判官席前審理，又指「除非你是黃色」，裁判官張天雁聞言，即指大律師不應在庭上說類似的說話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170609/56804723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170609%2F56804723&d=0s68vNj6VSRy7dwr4P3BhsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=51ac34b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170609%2F56804723&h=1581ff8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170609/56804723</a>"},{"pid":"309cb5eecf80fac7c73ffcb5ca5575c67f6955ce","tid":276840,"uid":63233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"820395bafe70f3f78b683e32d7b773d75e1fc4d1","tid":276840,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"黃絲呀"},{"pid":"43f02a592442db00685782369816e9ac38863cef","tid":276840,"uid":45213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃絲呀</blockquote><br />\n照做鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca7816e7e860cac6f5561c269d6ff378f24d0fb","tid":276840,"uid":1